{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0565b92165","title":"右派言论——攻击、丑化党员","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7c23b9fc5b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0565b92165"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0719097e5e","name":"李焕添"},{"id":"5634b105aa","name":"曾纪经"},{"id":"a772556365","name":"陈乙华"},{"id":"ad966f7ea5","name":"中山大学"},{"id":"b033c0891e","name":"吴重翰"},{"id":"d169219091","name":"杨支毅"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5f073298a7","type":"title","text":"右派言论——攻击、丑化党员","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"010c966fd1","type":"authors","text":"中山大学杨支毅陈乙华李焕添曾纪经吴重翰","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"ef36950955","type":"paragraph","text":"“对共产党我拥护，对某些党员我憎恨、鄙视，党员自以为是特殊材料制成的。如果有斯大林主义的话，那便是所谓特殊材料论，我不把党员看成是特殊材料制成的。”（中山大学　杨支毅）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"30d2d8a405","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在是官官相护，一个党员尽管是很坏的，一样可以当官，拿的钱比日夜辛苦的人多得多，且有‘生杀’之权。”（中山大学  陈乙华）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"acf2f01c2a","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在党的干部和国民党的官吏没有什么不同，高高在上，骑在人民头上，无恶不作。”（中山大学  李焕添）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"bfa0178cd0","type":"appellation","text":"“一些党员对待一些非党群众是冷酷无情，入了党就六亲不认。”（中山大学　曾纪经）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"8e35c08192","type":"paragraph","text":"“积极分子有两重性；当党的助手也当党的打手。”（中山大学  吴重翰）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"},{"id":"43f2155785","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"}],"page":{"id":"d9629a9d35","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0565b92165"